      Carole Park sits on the boundary between Brisbane City and Ipswich City, positioned alongside Darra, Wacol and Richlands with direct Ipswich Motorway access. It is a suburb that delivers freestanding homes on usable blocks at a price point that is consistently below comparable properties in Darra and Oxley.
    </p>
